  colors
  Builtin Function



      [1mSynopsis[0m
        Sets the terminal foreground and background color.  Resets the
        terminal color scheme to default values.

      [1mSyntax[0m
        colors ( [4mfg[24m, [4mbg[24m )

        colors ( )


      [1mArguments[0m

         [1mfg / bg[0m
           name of the color, "default", "red", "green", "yellow" or
           "brown", "blue", "magenta", "cyan", "grey" or "white".

         [1mnone[0m
           resets the terminal to its default values.


        colors uses termcap library.


     [1mSee Also[0m
        clrscr, mvcrsr, clrpos.




































